cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Provision of Paper Mapping Products for Tailte Éireann
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: Tailte Éireann are mandated to provide a national mapping service to the State. As part of our services, Tailte Éireann produce and sell paper mapping products and wish to outsource the printing of these products, as is current practice. Tailte Éireann invites tenderers for the provision of services relating to the provision of Paper Mapping Products
